Thank you for your interest in joining the team at Lynora’s! We’ve received your career inquiry and truly appreciate your enthusiasm for being part of our growing family.  Our hiring team reviews every submission carefully. If your experience and availability match one of our open roles, someone from our team will reach out directly to schedule a conversation.  In the meantime, feel free to follow us on Instagram  @LynorasRestaurant to get a taste of our culture and stay up to date with what’s happening at each of our locations.
